{"tid":919721,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【三代同堂】鼎爺施明再抱孫笑開顏 李泳豪晒溫馨全家福","createTime":"2018-11-28T09:12:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-12T05:23:05.000Z","uid":130626,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"4db9b274d52f7cb05bb485eba9e06045bcb989b7","tid":919721,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T09:12:19.000Z","msg":"李家鼎同前妻施明77年結婚，誕下孖仔李泳豪、李泳漢，94年時施明單方面申請離婚，原因係性格不合，不過鼎爺一直唔肯簽紙，施明單方面申請離婚後，就帶埋對孖仔移民美國。<br />\n李泳豪、李泳漢同爸爸嘅感情非常好，鼎爺同施明離咗婚多年，一直話希望同施明復合，到最後知道復合無望，終於放低舊情，年前遇到現任太太，結果再婚組織新家庭，反而施明感情仍然空白，多年嚟潛心向佛。<br />\n大家都各自有自己嘅生活，孖仔長大成人，李泳漢亦都結婚生咗對仔女，太太剛誕下細女Charlotte，湊個「好」字，只差泳豪未有着落。<br />\n鼎爺又做爺爺梗係開心啦！最近仲趁新抱坐完月，去咗影樓坐影全家福，今日泳豪喺instagram分享咗呢張全家福，有父母施明、鼎爺、細佬一家四口，留言：「三代同堂，齊齊整整，平平安安。幸福，感恩，珍惜。」相中見施明抱住孫女，鼎爺就抱住孫仔，大家都笑得好開心，真係好溫馨，而施明扮得好靚，更係明艷照人呀！<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181128/large/1543381185_2882.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181128%2Flarge%2F1543381185_2882.jpg&h=ec2ddb5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181128/large/1543381191_fba5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181128%2Flarge%2F1543381191_fba5.jpg&h=03fe16ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181128/large/1543381191_1069.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181128%2Flarge%2F1543381191_1069.jpg&h=ae06b18e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181128/large/1543381185_a019.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181128%2Flarge%2F1543381185_a019.jpg&h=ef6f8a83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20181128/58967777\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.c